headline: BD Names Pamela Spikner as Chief Accounting Officer and Controller
summary: BD (Becton, Dickinson and Company) (NYSE: BDX), a leading global medical technology company, announced today that Pamela Spikner has been named senior vice president, chief accounting officer and controller, effective January 20.
